[[Fenaɣ (alɩwaatʊ)|Fenasɩ]] naadozo hɛkʊ taa kɛna alɩwaatʊ taa alɩwaayʊʊ nakʊyʊ nɛ fenasɩ naadozo yaa nasɩdozo kpɛndʊna nɛ pɩla fenasɩ naadozo. Pʊtɔɔbʊʊ se fenasɩ naadozo hɛkʊ taa kʊɖʊmʊʊ taa lɛ, [[Kpɩtaʋ|kpɩtaŋ]] naanza wɛna. Pʊtɔbʊʊ se pɛtɛyɩ fenasɩ naadozo hɛkʊ taa kɛ nabudozo taa kɔyɔ fenaɣ kʊɖʊmaɣ panaɣ. 
* Pɩnaɣ taa kacalaɣ fenasɩ naadozo kɔyɔ: [[kɔlaɣ fenaɣ]], [[lɛlaɣ fenaɣ]] nɛ [[lakɩŋ fenaɣ]]. 
* Pɩnaɣ taa fenasɩ naadozo taa naalɛ ñɩnzɩ kɔyɔ: [[ɖomaɣ fenaɣ]], [[agoza fenaɣ]] nɛ [[Mɩsɩkʋm fenaɣ|mɩsɩkʊm fenaɣ]]. 
* Pɩnaɣ taa fenasɩ naadozo taa naadozo ñɩnzɩ kɔyɔ: [[hasɩyaɖɛ fenaɣ]], [[kɩyɛɛna fenaɣ]] nɛ [[salaŋ fenaɣ]]. 
* Pɩnaɣ taa fenasɩ naadozo kpaagbaa ñɩnzɩ kɔyɔ: [[aloma fenaɣ]], [[kamɩŋ fenaɣ]] nɛ [[saŋayɩŋ fenaɣ]].
Pʊtɔbʊʊ se, pɩnaɣ taa lɛ fenasɩ naadozo wɛ tɔm naanza taa.
